     | allowExternalSignaturePad                          | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, an external signature pad can be used for signing. The signature pad type is set by the externalSignaturePadType property.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    |
