     | allowMarkup                                        | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, the document markup feature is enabled for the account.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       |
