     | dataFieldRegexEnabled                              | Boolean | Admin                                                       | When **true**, the Regex field is available for tabs with that property.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
